Unified Pseudopotential Format
------------------------------

* Original code: ESPRESSO

* Used by:
   1) ESPRESSO
   2) Octopus
   3) ABINIT

*Generated by:
   1) ESPRESSO
   2) APE

* Notes:
   1) Format description at http://www.quantum-espresso.org/wiki/index.php/Unified_pseudopotential_format
   2) Does allow for relativistic j-dependent pseudopotentials.
   3) Includes KB projectors instead of pseudopotentials.
   4) Includes wavefunctions.
